=Description=

"[[Open Everything]] is a global conversation about the art, science and spirit of 'open'. It gathers people using openness to create and improve software, education, media, philanthropy, architecture, neighbourhoods, workplaces and the society we live in: everything. It's about thinking, doing and being open. This page is an introduction to all the Open Everything Events in the United States; as well as most recent Twitter Conversations around the issues related to the events."


